{"tid":2489362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"烏克蘭總統秘訪東部戰壕 鼓舞前線","createTime":"2021-04-15T02:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T02:13:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15b6a00da861ed59fdbd8538d5d2612f978238cb","tid":2489362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:02:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210414/YGRSNBSYGJEHFPQ63JHIKWT6YA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210414%2FYGRSNBSYGJEHFPQ63JHIKWT6YA%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=86b2b5ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210414%2FYGRSNBSYGJEHFPQ63JHIKWT6YA%2F&h=53fe7184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210414/YGRSNBSYGJEHFPQ63JHIKWT6YA/</a><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭總統秘訪東部戰壕 鼓舞前線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m7RLbsdoy_dQu0KXTkFq7uFU9gA=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WOQMPQHITJAJPBXMMA7SKSYRM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm7RLbsdoy_dQu0KXTkFq7uFU9gA%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWOQMPQHITJAJPBXMMA7SKSYRM4.jpg&h=23536ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■烏克蘭總統澤連斯基（右）日前到訪東部衝突前線。路透社<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭東部衝突近日升溫，俄羅斯又在接壤的邊境集結八萬大軍，令烏國和西方大為緊張。烏克蘭總統澤連斯基日前秘訪東部戰壕，為前線士兵打氣。<br />\n<br />\n身穿迷彩防彈背心和頭盔的澤連斯基，在一批保鑣和軍人陪同下造訪馬里烏波爾前線，當地今年有逾20名烏軍中了疑受俄訓練的狙擊手冷槍死亡，澤連斯基一行人在空地奔跑至戰壕尋掩護。他向特邀採訪的美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）記者稱，他堅持要到最前線：「如果我只訪問軍事基地，最前線的人聽到，就會認為我忘了他們。他們需要知道有得到政治支持。」<br />\n<br />\n澤連斯基發言人指俄近日在近烏東邊境和克里米亞，分別聚集四萬軍人，又指澤連斯基上月底已要求跟俄總統普京通電話，但一直無回音。克里姆林宮稱沒收到要求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析指俄無意開戰<br />\n<br />\n俄稱無計劃入侵烏克蘭，但警告會出手保護烏東的俄公民，昨指美國派兩軍艦赴黑海協防烏國是挑釁，警告勿近克里米亞。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"c684887d7f5a4519d3f698cb6ac23924626d8f6d","tid":2489362,"uid":70846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"屌 型過普京喎呢張相"},{"pid":"ca589b67609f0f00d5f9b560b73727afa9801c96","tid":2489362,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c684887d7f5a4519d3f698cb6ac23924626d8f6d","tid":2489362,"uid":70846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"屌 型過普京喎呢張相"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"普京係RGB只係做過文官 強人個image只係PR既一部分"},{"pid":"3a55d2ea381cb030f8ca6e15e93d5ec682060e0f","tid":2489362,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca589b67609f0f00d5f9b560b73727afa9801c96","tid":2489362,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c684887d7f5a4519d3f698cb6ac23924626d8f6d","tid":2489362,"uid":70846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"屌 型過普京喎呢張相"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"普京係RGB只係做過文官 強人個image只係PR既一部分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"打錯係KGB"},{"pid":"105802b4b2ff0b1e4307c07dc52b2f01ad3b60b1","tid":2489362,"uid":322732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"戰時總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}